The paper deals with belief base revision, which is a topic in artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of Unified Answer Set Programs (UASP) is a logical framework that falls under the category of logic in computer science (cs.LO). The paper also deals with nonmonotonic reasoning, which is a subfield of logic programming (cs.PL). The strategy used for base revision, Removed Set Revision, is a technique used in cryptography and security (cs.CR). Finally, the paper deals with uncertain and imprecise information, which is a topic in data structures and algorithms (cs.DS).
